Data Sources
------------
This repository compiles publicly available neuroimaging datasets:

1. Human Connectome Project (HCP) — WU-Minn Consortium
   URL: https://www.humanconnectome.org/
   License: HCP Open Access Data Use Terms

2. OpenNeuro — BIDS-formatted neuroimaging datasets
   URL: https://openneuro.org/
   License: CC0 / CC BY 4.0 (per dataset)

3. NeuroVault — Statistical Brain Maps
   URL: https://neurovault.org/
   License: CC0

4. Brainnetome Atlas — Institute of Automation, CAS
   URL: https://atlas.brainnetome.org/
   License: Free for research use

